{"word":"ἔκγονος","slug":"ἔκγονος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἔϰγονος, ον</el></b> [<el>ἐϰγίγνομαι</el> ‘be born of’; offspring as ‘son/daughter’, also ‘grandchild’] ‘in descent from’, as noun <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a></el> or <el>ἡ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔκγονος\">ἔκγονος</a></el>, specifically <b>grandchild <a href='B:610 5:4'>1 Ti 5:4</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκγαμίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκδαπανάω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}